<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.8.8">
<l>ulaka mēttu moruva ṉeṉṟu moṇcu ṭarō ṭumpa reytā</l>
<l>nilavu māḻip paṭaiya ṉeṉṟum nēca ṉeṉṟun teṉti caikkut</l>
<l>tilata maṉṉa maṟaiyōr nāṅkait tēva tēva ṉeṉṟeṉ ṟōti</l>
<l>palaru mēca veṉma ṭantai pārttaṉ paḷḷi pāṭu vāḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying, “The one whom the world praises,” saying, “Friend,”</l>
<l>Saying, “The one with the discus weapon which shines</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the brilliant sun and the gods [can]not approach,”</l>
<l>Reciting over and over, “God of gods in Nāṅkai, [where dwell] Vedic experts,</l>
<l rend="indent">[which is] like a tilaka for the southern region,”</l>
<l>So that many scorn [her], my simple girl sings of Pārttaṉpaḷḷi.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
